# To further unleash the potential of graph for RAG, we propose NodeRAG, a graph-centric framework introducing heterogeneous graph structures that enable the seamless and holistic integration of graph-based methodologies into the RAG workflow.
@article{noderag,
  title={NodeRAG: Structuring graph-based rag with heterogeneous nodes},
  author={Xu, Tianyang and Zheng, Haojie and Li, Chengze and Chen, Haoxiang and Liu, Yixin and Chen, Ruoxi and Sun, Lichao},
